<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MEI Deliveries</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        header{
            color: #5FC9BF;
        }
        .carousel-item img {
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            object-fit: cover; 
            filter: brightness(0.9);
        }

        .carousel-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03));
            z-index: 1; 
        }

        .carousel-caption {
            color: white; /* Set text color to white */
        }

        .carousel-caption h5,
        .carousel-caption p {
                color: white !important; /* Ensures all caption text is white */
         }

        .about-us, .how-to-order {
            padding-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            
        }

        .about-us {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
        }

        .how-to-order {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; 
            
        }

        .section-title {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #5FC9BF;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="text-center my-4">
        <h1 style="color: #5FC9BF; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to MEI Deliveries! 🍕🚀</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #555;">Craving something delicious? We've got you covered! From sizzling steaks to cheesy pizzas, your next meal is just a click away. Order now and let the feast come to you! 🍔🍣🥞</p>
    </header>
    <!-- Carousel -->
    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="4" aria-label="Slide 5"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="https://grandwesternsteaks.com/media/catalog/product/cache/c4a8b97347133f8bf6df5ac55676bb3c/s/h/shutterstock_1776899162.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Grilled Steak">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Premium Steaks</h5>
                    <p>Indulge in perfectly grilled, tender steaks with rich flavors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://azulflojito.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/qq3ht-cyd1i-1024x683.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Delicious Pancakes">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Irresistible Pancakes</h5>
                    <p>Fluffy, golden pancakes topped with fresh fruits and syrup.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://mozartcultures.com/en/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Borracha_overhead.11.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Mexican Food">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Authentic Mexican Cuisine</h5>
                    <p>Enjoy the bold flavors of tacos, burritos, and spicy salsas.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571091718767-18b5b1457add" class="d-block w-100" alt="Juicy Burgers">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Juicy Burgers</h5>
                    <p>Savor our handcrafted, juicy burgers with fresh ingredients.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://c4.wallpaperflare.com/wallpaper/1005/1000/931/delicious-pizza-pepperoni-pizza-wallpaper-preview.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Delicious Pizza">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Delicious Pizza</h5>
                    <p>Enjoy cheesy, oven-baked pizza with your favorite toppings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>



    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
          
            <div class="col-md-6 about-us">
                <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
                <p>Welcome to MEI Deliveries, where great food meets unbeatable convenience! We bring your favorite meals from the best local restaurants straight to your doorstep—hot, fresh, and fast.</p>
                <p>Our mission is simple: to turn every meal into a delightful experience. With an easy-to-use platform, real-time order tracking, and a wide variety of cuisines, we make sure your cravings are always satisfied. Whether you're in the mood for comfort food, a healthy bite, or an indulgent treat, we've got you covered.</p>
                <p>At MEI Deliveries, quality and customer satisfaction come first. We handpick our restaurant partners to ensure every dish meets your expectations. So sit back, relax, and let us bring the feast to you.!</p>
                <h6>🚀 Fast. Fresh. Flavorful. That’s the MEI Deliveries promise.</h6>
                <p>Thanks for choosing us—we can’t wait to serve you! </p>
            </div>

           
            <div class="col-md-6 how-to-order">
                <h2 class="section-title">How to Order</h2>
                <p>1️⃣ Sign Up & Log In – Create an account or log in to get started.</p>
                <p>2️⃣ Pick Your Favorite Restaurant – Browse a variety of restaurants and find your cravings.</p>
                <p>3️⃣ Fill Your Cart – Select delicious meals and add them to your shopping cart.</p>
                <p>4️⃣ Enter Your Details – Provide your delivery address and phone number for a smooth experience.</p>
                <p>5️⃣ Place Your Order & Relax – Sit back and let us handle the rest while your food makes its way to you!</p>
                <h5>Bon appétit! 🍽🚀</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.3.0/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
